readme: |
  For Raycast extension work, start by reading `docs/raycast-dev.md`.
  - Use local extensions (not Script Commands) unless explicitly requested.
  - Validate manifests with `npx @raycast/api lint` and build with `npx @raycast/api dev`.
  - Icons must be PNG 512x512 in `assets/icon.png`.

conventions:
  - extensions_have:
      - src/
      - assets/icon.png
      - README.md
      - package.json with root-level Raycast fields

priority_files:
  - docs/raycast-dev.md
  - **/package.json
  - **/src/**/*.tsx







